Package: autofocus
Type: Package
Title: AutoFocus: A hierarchical framework to explore multi-omic disease associations 
    spanning multiple scales of biomolecular interaction
Version: 1.0.0
Author: c(
    person("Annalise", "Schweickart", email="aas4002@med.cornell.edu", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kelsey", "Chetnik", role=c("aut")))
Description: Companion package to the publication of the same name. This package provides a 
    convenient functionality for running the autofocus method and for visualizing the 
    generated hierarchical framework.
